      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a reliable daily driver for someone comfortable with a few imperfections. The exterior shows its age with some noticeable scratches, minor dings, and fading clear coat on the roof, while the interior has visible wear on the upholstery and a few cracked plastic trim pieces. Mechanically, the car starts and runs consistently, though it will likely need new tires and a brake service in the near future. It is a solid, functional vehicle that provides dependable transportation but lacks the polish of a newer or better-maintained model.",
