      "description": "This vehicle is in truly mint condition, appearing and driving as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep shine, and the interior is pristine with no signs of wear. Every mechanical component functions perfectly, and the car has been meticulously maintained with a full service history available.",
