      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting a rare opportunity to own a collector-grade specimen in pristine condition. This vehicle has been meticulously preserved to maintain its original showroom brilliance, offering a driving experience that feels indistinguishable from new. Every surface, from the flawless exterior to the untouched interior, reflects a standard of care rarely seen on the market. For the discerning buyer who demands absolute perfection and long-term value, this vehicle stands as a benchmark of automotive excellence.",
